{"tid":1851723,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[集思廣益] 立即封關 我要口罩 香港獨立","createTime":"2020-01-30T06:45:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-30T06:45:07.000Z","uid":279513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"725534dd483cd67a2dbd471347e206f571f9b7ce","tid":1851723,"uid":279513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T06:45:07.000Z","msg":"而家柒婆唔封關搞到全城搶口罩, 又搞到醫護手足全部火起<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">當然最好就係宣傳香港獨立<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span><br />\n不如一人一句獨立口號, 同埋一人一條獨立文宣Q&amp;A?<br />\n<br />\n由於口號多數係第二句大聲少少, 所以大家設計時要重點喺後面<br />\n光復香港<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">時代革命</span><br />\n五大訴求<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">缺一不可</span><br />\n<br />\n口號設計我先<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />:<br />\n立即封關 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港獨立</span><br />\n我要口罩 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">兩國兩制</span><br />\n抵制支那 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我要獨立</span><br />\n<br />\nQ&amp;A有少少難諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />:<br />\n<br />\nQ: 點解要香港獨立?<br />\nA: 獨立左咪可以封關, 禁止肺炎生化武器黎香港<br />\n<br />\nQ: 我有好多親戚喺中國喎, 點可以分開兩個國家?<br />\nA: 我都有好多親戚喺英國美國加拿大澳洲架<br />\n<br />\nQ: 獨立左邊個當兵? 你班廢青去做呀?<br />\nA: 香港以前都有用啹咖兵, 初初都係比錢請返黎. 好多國家例如波蘭都係比錢美軍做國防<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">康復香港 時代抗疫<br />\n願榮光歸香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n黑警死全家 條屍比狗咬</span></span></strong>"}]}